    "He was awarded the <a href=\"/matherf\">Frank Jewett Mather, Jr.</a>, Award for Distinction in Art Criticism in 1981.": [],
    "In 1984 two books appeared, <em>Modern Painting and the Northern Romantic Tradition</em> and the survey <em>Art of the Nineteenth Century</em>, the second co-authored with fellow NYU faculty <a href=\"/jansonh\">Horst Woldemar Janson</a>.": [],
    "In 1989 Rosenblum published his controversial <em>Paintings in the Musee d'Orsay</em>, a revisionist view of 19th-century art incorporating C\u00e9zanne, Manet and other mainstream avant-garde greats, along with previously disparaged academic artists such as William Bouguereau, in order to paint the larger picture of the art milieu.": [
